WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.941
Welcome to your RestoreAssist dashboard.

00:05.941 --> 00:13.941
Here you can see your active jobs, recent inspections, team activity, and key metrics at a glance.

00:13.941 --> 00:21.941
Use the sidebar to navigate between modules, or search for anything from the top bar.

00:21.941 --> 00:29.941
The quick action buttons let you create an inspection, generate a report, or invite a team member in one click.

00:29.941 --> 00:37.941
Your workspace health score tells you everything is running optimally.